      "content": "Building on his excellent jump skills, the boy dashes across the vibrant green lawn. Chasing a bright beach ball toward him, he displays spectacular agility past the flowers and white picket fence. Exhilarated by his impressive speed, he shouts with joy: \"Look at me! I can run!\"",
